  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Single line message and timestamp should be displayed in single line if there is enough space. See message \"1\" and its timestamp look like on iPhone X (11.2.1):\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7532782/41964493-6c4d4cd2-79fa-11e8-9593-ba27c57a0287.png\" width=\"200\">\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nThe message and timestamp are displayed in single line if there is enough space.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nThe message and timestamp were displayed in 2 lines.\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: 0.9.21\r\n* Issue experienced on: iPhone X, 11.2.1\r\n* Could not be reproduced on: Galaxy S8, iPhone 8\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n",
